  portrait:
    formats: [webp, jpg]
    crop: '2:3'
    widths: [300, 400, 600, 800, 1000]
    sizes:
      mobile: 100vw
      tablet: 50vw
      desktop: 33vw
    fallback_width: 600
    fallback_format: jpg
    attributes:
      picture: 'class="portrait-image"'
      img: 'loading="lazy"'

  # Wide images (16:9)
  wide:
    formats: [webp, jpg]
    crop: '16:9'
    widths: [600, 800, 1000, 1200, 1600, 1920]
    sizes:
      mobile: 100vw
      tablet: 100vw
      desktop: 90vw
    fallback_width: 1200
    fallback_format: jpg
    attributes:
      picture: 'class="wide-image"'
      img: 'loading="lazy"'

  # ===========================
  # SPECIALIZED PRESETS
  # ===========================

  # Avatar/Profile pictures
  avatar:
    formats: [webp, jpg]
    crop: '1:1'
    widths: [80, 120, 160, 240]
    sizes:
      mobile: 80px
      tablet: 120px
      desktop: 160px
    quality:
      webp: 90
      jpg: 90
    fallback_width: 160
    fallback_format: jpg
    attributes:
      picture: 'class="avatar"'
      img: 'loading="lazy"'

  # Blog post featured image
  post_featured:
    formats: [webp, jpg]
    crop: '3:2'
    widths: [600, 800, 1000, 1200, 1600]
    sizes:
      mobile: 100vw
      tablet: 100vw
      desktop: 800px
    quality:
      webp: 88
      jpg: 88
    fallback_width: 1200
    fallback_format: jpg
    attributes:
      picture: 'class="post-featured-image"'
      img: 'loading="eager"'

  # High quality for photography
  photography:
    formats: [webp, jpg]
    widths: [800, 1200, 1600, 2000, 2400]
    sizes:
      mobile: 100vw
      tablet: 100vw
      desktop: 100vw
    quality:
      webp: 95
      jpg: 95
    fallback_width: 1600
    fallback_format: jpg
    attributes:
      picture: 'class="photography"'
      img: 'loading="lazy"'



Basic responsive image:
liquid{% picture default path/to/image.jpg alt="Description" %}
3:2 cropped responsive image:
liquid{% picture crop_3x2 path/to/image.jpg alt="Description" %}
Hero image with 3:2 aspect ratio:
liquid{% picture hero_3x2 path/to/hero.jpg alt="Hero description" %}
Card/thumbnail with 3:2 crop:
liquid{% picture card_3x2 path/to/card-image.jpg alt="Card image" %}
Gallery images:
liquid{% picture gallery path/to/gallery-image.jpg alt="Gallery item" %}

Key Features:
3:2 Aspect Ratio Presets:

crop_3x2 - General responsive 3:2 cropped images
hero_3x2 - Large hero/banner images in 3:2
card_3x2 - Card/preview images in 3:2
thumb_3x2 - Small thumbnails in 3:2

General Responsive Presets:

default - Standard responsive images (no crop)
hero - Full-width hero images
content - Images within text content
thumbnail - Small preview images
gallery - Grid layout images

Other Aspect Ratios:

square (1:1), portrait (2:3), wide (16:9)

Specialized:

avatar - Profile pictures
post_featured - Blog featured images
photography - High-quality preservation

All presets include WebP and JPG formats with lazy loading by default (except heroes which use eager loading).
